  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/c10a5f40308b0fdefb955190f98025fc.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/c10a5f40308b0fdefb955190f98025fc.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/c10a5f40308b0fdefb955190f98025fc.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Below Surface is a game about a job offer with a strict contract where employees are in charge of controlling a specialized robot to navigate a supernatural mineshaft and to collect ores from the cave, and put them into minecarts for selling. You will also have to deal with the constantly changing layout of the cave.<br><br>The inhabitants of the cave will also be a problem, however, this robot is specially made to handle everything you’ll encounter. It has lots of utilities that make it much easier to get your tasks done with minimal trouble:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/05e755c5edcbe4b6d3126955a2baeca9.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/05e755c5edcbe4b6d3126955a2baeca9.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/05e755c5edcbe4b6d3126955a2baeca9.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your pickaxe not only can be used for breaking ores, but it can also be used as a tactical weapon against smaller creatures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/493eecfdde7aa2f499004e96eaaea728.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/493eecfdde7aa2f499004e96eaaea728.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/493eecfdde7aa2f499004e96eaaea728.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you need to move quick, sliding allows you to not only move faster but to maintain momentum.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/acfc9e5a9947b8407756e1804d041478.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/acfc9e5a9947b8407756e1804d041478.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/acfc9e5a9947b8407756e1804d041478.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There is nothing that is out of your reach. You can scale just about anything with wall jumping.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/c10a5f40308b0fdefb955190f98025fc.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/c10a5f40308b0fdefb955190f98025fc.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/c10a5f40308b0fdefb955190f98025fc.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Below Surface is a game about a job offer with a strict contract where employees are in charge of controlling a specialized robot to navigate a supernatural mineshaft and to collect ores from the cave, and put them into minecarts for selling. You will also have to deal with the constantly changing layout of the cave.<br><br>The inhabitants of the cave will also be a problem, however, this robot is specially made to handle everything you’ll encounter. It has lots of utilities that make it much easier to get your tasks done with minimal trouble:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/05e755c5edcbe4b6d3126955a2baeca9.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/05e755c5edcbe4b6d3126955a2baeca9.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/05e755c5edcbe4b6d3126955a2baeca9.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your pickaxe not only can be used for breaking ores, but it can also be used as a tactical weapon against smaller creatures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/493eecfdde7aa2f499004e96eaaea728.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/493eecfdde7aa2f499004e96eaaea728.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/493eecfdde7aa2f499004e96eaaea728.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you need to move quick, sliding allows you to not only move faster but to maintain momentum.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/acfc9e5a9947b8407756e1804d041478.poster.avif?t=1715218221\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/acfc9e5a9947b8407756e1804d041478.webm?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841000/extras/acfc9e5a9947b8407756e1804d041478.mp4?t=1715218221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There is nothing that is out of your reach. You can scale just about anything with wall jumping.",
